"                        println!(\\\"cargo:rustc-link-lib=bz2\\\");~@@\n"
"                        @}~%\"))))))\n"
msgstr ""
"(rust-bzip2-sys-0.1.13+1.0.8 ஐ வரையறுக்கவும் \n"
"(crate-source \"bzip2-sys\" \"0.1.13+1.0.8\" \n"
